sub_title: Executive Supply Chain professional / Change agent /  Bridge builder
summary:
Experienced turnaround manager, in both developed and less developed markets. People manager, demanding, good sense of humor, worked and lived in various countries in the Caribbean, Central and Latin America, Africa, Europe and am currently based in the Netherlands. 

I am grateful to have worked for Heineken in various continents, living in many countries with my wife and daughters. Now I am enjoying a sabbatical break and honestly enjoying this very much :)
